<item>
            <title>[LU-8286] kernel BUG at fs/inode.c:1358!</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8286</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Is duplicate of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6911&quot; title=&quot;sanity 102ha test failed: mds crash kernel BUG at fs/inode.c:1358! RIP [&amp;lt;ffffffff811a53c9&amp;gt;] iput+0x69/0x70&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-6911&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-6911&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. But we need back port to 2.5.3 and 2.7&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;MDS crash with error.&lt;br/&gt;
Rebooted mds and ran fsck on mdt.&lt;br/&gt;
After recovery it crashed again&lt;br/&gt;
Rebooted mds after recovery it crashed again same spot!&lt;br/&gt;
System is currently DOWN&lt;/p&gt;

